{
    "text": " Good morning everyone, thank you for joining today's project planning meeting. Our objective is to finalize the timeline for the AI meeting and diligent system and assigned responsibilities for the first development sprint. Good morning, I have completed the initial research on the speech recognition models. I recommend using open AI whisper because it provides accurate transcription and works well even with the background noise. That sounds good. I will start working on the backend APIs that will process the transcript and communicate with the AI models. I expect to finish the API development by next Monday. From the design perspective, I have prepared a few dashboard wireframes. The dashboard will display the meeting transcript, AI generated summary, action items, sentiment analysis and productivity score in a clean and user friendly layout. Excellent, we also need to make sure that the streamlit application is responsive and easy to use. Please keep the interface simple because our target users are business professionals. I also suggest adding automatic meeting summaries using transformer based language models. This feature will help user quickly understand the importance discussion points without reading the complete transcript. We should also include an action item extractor that automatically identifies assigned task, responsible team members and deadlines that will improve productivity and reduce manual note-taking. I agree, we can also visualize meeting statistics such as speaking time, positive sentiment, percentage and the overall meeting productivity scores using charts. That's a great idea. Our deadline for completing the first prototype is next Friday before that everyone should push their latest code to the GitHub and update the project documentation. I will also perform testing on different meeting records to verify the transcription accuracy and ensure the summaries are meaningful. If everything goes according to plan, we should be ready for the client demonstration next Tuesday. I will finalize the dashboard designed by Thursday and share it with the team for feedback. Perfect, thank you everyone. Let's stay on the schedule, communicate regularly and deliver a high quality prototype. The meeting is now concluded.",
